{
  "stem": "1775.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Now we know how wrong we were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "They took us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "At that particular time, they called different sections from-- where people used to work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "They called out, you work for this and this company, you come here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "You work for this and this company, you come here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "So people that had, had those permits to work went on the site.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And the other people, they used to just shut into the-- what do you call it-- in the crowd.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And I saw a lady lose her arm.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And it-- there-- with, you know, it fell down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And different people got wounded.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And nobody paid any attention to nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "They just-- people tried to get off that marketplace to the places where they were working.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And I guess I was fortunate to be taken off at that time for work, and so was my cousin and her mother and my brother.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And we went to the [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "Zuckerman's ?] tannery.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And we spent there all week because for the whole week, they were just grabbing people and sending them away.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And nobody-- I guess they, they killed them because you never saw them again.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And all the people that went with the first action, a lot of them died just in the trains on the way there because they were stuffed.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "They put in that white stuff.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "I forgot what it's called.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "It's-- and it just killed the people from the odor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "And the people, a lot of them, they went to Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "And then a few of them came back to our town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And they started to tell the horrors, what was going on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "Up until then, there was no ghetto in Miedzyrzec.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "After this first action, they made a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
